'''2021年克馬得群島地震'''是在2021年3月5日发生於紐西蘭[[克马德克群岛|克马德克群岛]]的地震。地震強度為8.1[[矩震級|矩震級]]。震央位于克馬得群島的[[拉烏爾島|拉烏爾島]]以南。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=M 8.1 - Kermadec Islands region|url=https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/pt21063003/executive|accessdate=2021-03-04|work=USGS-ANSS|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317043619/https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/pt21063003/executive|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中有前震為7.4級<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=M 7.4 - Kermadec Islands, New Zealand|url=https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/us7000dfk3/executive|accessdate=2021-03-04|work=USGS-ANSS|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411232752/https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/us7000dfk3/executive|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，有餘震為6.1級。<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=M 6.1 - Kermadec Islands region|url=https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/us7000dfmf/executive|accessdate=2021-03-04|work=USGS-ANSS|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317043625/https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/us7000dfmf/executive|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 地震 ==
這次的[[大型逆衝區地震|大型逆衝區地震]]由於反向斷層而沿[[隱沒帶|隱沒帶]]發生。[[美國地質調查局|美國地質調查局]]估計破裂區範圍達175×75公里。<ref name=":0" />前震發生在主震發生前的不到兩個小時。<ref name=":1" />在主震發生前大約6個小時，[[北島_(紐西蘭)|北岛]]亦发生了7.3级地震<ref>{{cite web|title=M 7.3 - 174 km NE of Gisborne, New Zealand|url=https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/us7000dffl/executive|date=2020-03-04|website=USGS|access-date=2020-03-05|archive-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404115702/https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/us7000dffl/executive|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但其被认为與此地震無關。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":2" />

== 海嘯 ==
地震發生後，[[太平洋|太平洋地區]]各地都發出了[[海啸|海啸]]警告，新西兰北岛則已受到海啸的威胁。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Live: 'Try and stay calm' says emergency management minister, tsunami waves expected for 'several hours' after earthquake|url=https://www.stuff.co.nz/national/300245006/live-try-and-stay-calm-says-emergency-management-minister-tsunami-waves-expected-for-several-hours-after-earthquake|accessdate=2021-03-04|date=2021-03-04|work=Stuff|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304234619/https://www.stuff.co.nz/national/300245006/live-try-and-stay-calm-says-emergency-management-minister-tsunami-waves-expected-for-several-hours-after-earthquake|dead-url=no}}</ref>數千名新西蘭居民需要到高地暫避。<ref name="9News">{{cite news|url=https://www.9news.com.au/world/new-zealand-earthquake-tsunami-warning-powerful-quake-off-northeast-coast/61b590ce-cb0e-4b01-bf34-320ffa183bcc|title=Tsunami threat passes in New Zealand, as evacuees allowed to return|first=Nick|last=Pearson|work=9 News|date=2020-03-05|access-date=2020-03-05|archive-date=2021-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424032916/https://www.9news.com.au/world/new-zealand-earthquake-tsunami-warning-powerful-quake-off-northeast-coast/61b590ce-cb0e-4b01-bf34-320ffa183bcc|dead-url=no}}</ref>到目前为止，根據GeoNet测得的數據，在{{Link-en|東角 (紐西蘭)|East Cape|東角}}的海嘯高度為大約{{Convert|35-40|cm|in}}，在[[大巴里爾島|大堡礁岛]]的海嘯高度則為{{Convert|15-20|cm|in}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=GeoNet News|url=https://www.geonet.org.nz/news/2SEHsNpMPFY7LyLkduIPNJ|accessdate=2021-03-05|work=www.geonet.org.nz|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424032924/https://www.geonet.org.nz/news/2SEHsNpMPFY7LyLkduIPNJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>

